  421. and payload i ppf = function
  422.   | PStr x -> structure i ppf x

  426.   | PPat (x, Some g) ->
  427.     pattern i ppf x;

  445. and type_extension i ppf x =

  447.   attributes i ppf x.ptyext_attributes;
  448.   let i = i+1 in
  449.   line i ppf "ptyext_path = %a\n" fmt_longident_loc x.ptyext_path;
  450.   line i ppf "ptyext_params =\n";
  451.   list (i+1) type_parameter ppf x.ptyext_params;
  452.   line i ppf "ptyext_constructors =\n";
  453.   list (i+1) extension_constructor ppf x.ptyext_constructors;
  454.   line i ppf "ptyext_private = %a\n" fmt_private_flag x.ptyext_private;

  456. and type_exception i ppf x =
  457.   line i ppf "type_exception\n";
  458.   attributes i ppf x.ptyexn_attributes;
  459.   let i = i+1 in
  460.   line i ppf "ptyext_constructor =\n";
  461.   let i = i+1 in
  462.   extension_constructor i ppf x.ptyexn_constructor

  464. and extension_constructor i ppf x =
  465.   line i ppf "extension_constructor %a\n" fmt_location x.pext_loc;
  466.   attributes i ppf x.pext_attributes;
  467.   let i = i + 1 in
  468.   line i ppf "pext_name = \"%s\"\n" x.pext_name.txt;
  469.   line i ppf "pext_kind =\n";
  470.   extension_constructor_kind (i + 1) ppf x.pext_kind;

  472. and extension_constructor_kind i ppf x =
  473.   match x with
  474.       Pext_decl(v, a, r) ->
  475.         line i ppf "Pext_decl\n";
  476.         if v <> [] then line (i+1) ppf "vars%a\n" typevars v;
  477.         constructor_arguments (i+1) ppf a;
  478.         option (i+1) core_type ppf r;
  479.     | Pext_rebind li ->
  480.         line i ppf "Pext_rebind\n";
  481.         line (i+1) ppf "%a\n" fmt_longident_loc li;

  483. and class_type i ppf x =
  484.   line i ppf "class_type %a\n" fmt_location x.pcty_loc;
  485.   attributes i ppf x.pcty_attributes;
  486.   let i = i+1 in
  487.   match x.pcty_desc with
  488.   | Pcty_constr (li, l) ->
  489.       line i ppf "Pcty_constr %a\n" fmt_longident_loc li;
  490.       list i core_type ppf l;
  491.   | Pcty_signature (cs) ->
  492.       line i ppf "Pcty_signature\n";
  493.       class_signature i ppf cs;
  494.   | Pcty_arrow (l, co, cl) ->
  495.       line i ppf "Pcty_arrow\n";
  496.       arg_label i ppf l;
  497.       core_type i ppf co;
  498.       class_type i ppf cl;
  499.   | Pcty_extension (s, arg) ->
  500.       line i ppf "Pcty_extension \"%s\"\n" s.txt;
  501.       payload i ppf arg
  502.   | Pcty_open (o, e) ->
  503.       line i ppf "Pcty_open %a %a\n" fmt_override_flag o.popen_override
  504.         fmt_longident_loc o.popen_expr;
  505.       class_type i ppf e

  507. and class_signature i ppf cs =
  508.   line i ppf "class_signature\n";
  509.   core_type (i+1) ppf cs.pcsig_self;
  510.   list (i+1) class_type_field ppf cs.pcsig_fields;

  512. and class_type_field i ppf x =
  513.   line i ppf "class_type_field %a\n" fmt_location x.pctf_loc;
  514.   let i = i+1 in
  515.   attributes i ppf x.pctf_attributes;
  516.   match x.pctf_desc with
  517.   | Pctf_inherit (ct) ->
  518.       line i ppf "Pctf_inherit\n";
  519.       class_type i ppf ct;
  520.   | Pctf_val (s, mf, vf, ct) ->
  521.       line i ppf "Pctf_val \"%s\" %a %a\n" s.txt fmt_mutable_flag mf
  522.            fmt_virtual_flag vf;
  523.       core_type (i+1) ppf ct;
  524.   | Pctf_method (s, pf, vf, ct) ->
  525.       line i ppf "Pctf_method \"%s\" %a %a\n" s.txt fmt_private_flag pf
  526.            fmt_virtual_flag vf;
  527.       core_type (i+1) ppf ct;
  528.   | Pctf_constraint (ct1, ct2) ->
  529.       line i ppf "Pctf_constraint\n";
  530.       core_type (i+1) ppf ct1;
  531.       core_type (i+1) ppf ct2;
  532.   | Pctf_attribute a ->
  533.       attribute i ppf "Pctf_attribute" a
  534.   | Pctf_extension (s, arg) ->
  535.       line i ppf "Pctf_extension \"%s\"\n" s.txt;
  536.      payload i ppf arg

  538. and class_description i ppf x =
  539.   line i ppf "class_description %a\n" fmt_location x.pci_loc;
  540.   attributes i ppf x.pci_attributes;
  541.   let i = i+1 in
  542.   line i ppf "pci_virt = %a\n" fmt_virtual_flag x.pci_virt;
  543.   line i ppf "pci_params =\n";
  544.   list (i+1) type_parameter ppf x.pci_params;
  545.   line i ppf "pci_name = %a\n" fmt_string_loc x.pci_name;
  546.   line i ppf "pci_expr =\n";
  547.   class_type (i+1) ppf x.pci_expr;

  549. and class_type_declaration i ppf x =
  550.   line i ppf "class_type_declaration %a\n" fmt_location x.pci_loc;
  551.   attributes i ppf x.pci_attributes;
  552.   let i = i+1 in
  553.   line i ppf "pci_virt = %a\n" fmt_virtual_flag x.pci_virt;
  554.   line i ppf "pci_params =\n";
  555.   list (i+1) type_parameter ppf x.pci_params;
  556.   line i ppf "pci_name = %a\n" fmt_string_loc x.pci_name;
  557.   line i ppf "pci_expr =\n";
  558.   class_type (i+1) ppf x.pci_expr;

  560. and class_expr i ppf x =
  561.   line i ppf "class_expr %a\n" fmt_location x.pcl_loc;
  562.   attributes i ppf x.pcl_attributes;
  563.   let i = i+1 in
  564.   match x.pcl_desc with
  565.   | Pcl_constr (li, l) ->
  566.       line i ppf "Pcl_constr %a\n" fmt_longident_loc li;
  567.       list i core_type ppf l;
  568.   | Pcl_structure (cs) ->
  569.       line i ppf "Pcl_structure\n";
  570.       class_structure i ppf cs;
  571.   | Pcl_fun (l, eo, p, e) ->
  572.       line i ppf "Pcl_fun\n";
  573.       arg_label i ppf l;
  574.       option i expression ppf eo;
  575.       pattern i ppf p;
  576.       class_expr i ppf e;
  577.   | Pcl_apply (ce, l) ->
  578.       line i ppf "Pcl_apply\n";
  579.       class_expr i ppf ce;
  580.       list i label_x_expression ppf l;
  581.   | Pcl_let (rf, l, ce) ->
  582.       line i ppf "Pcl_let %a\n" fmt_rec_flag rf;
  583.       list i value_binding ppf l;
  584.       class_expr i ppf ce;
  585.   | Pcl_constraint (ce, ct) ->
  586.       line i ppf "Pcl_constraint\n";
  587.       class_expr i ppf ce;
  588.       class_type i ppf ct;
  589.   | Pcl_extension (s, arg) ->
  590.       line i ppf "Pcl_extension \"%s\"\n" s.txt;
  591.       payload i ppf arg
  592.   | Pcl_open (o, e) ->
  593.       line i ppf "Pcl_open %a %a\n" fmt_override_flag o.popen_override
  594.         fmt_longident_loc o.popen_expr;
  595.       class_expr i ppf e

  597. and class_structure i ppf { pcstr_self = p; pcstr_fields = l } =
  598.   line i ppf "class_structure\n";
  599.   pattern (i+1) ppf p;
  600.   list (i+1) class_field ppf l;

  602. and class_field i ppf x =
  603.   line i ppf "class_field %a\n" fmt_location x.pcf_loc;
  604.   let i = i + 1 in
  605.   attributes i ppf x.pcf_attributes;
  606.   match x.pcf_desc with
  607.   | Pcf_inherit (ovf, ce, so) ->
  608.       line i ppf "Pcf_inherit %a\n" fmt_override_flag ovf;
  609.       class_expr (i+1) ppf ce;
  610.       option (i+1) string_loc ppf so;
  611.   | Pcf_val (s, mf, k) ->
  612.       line i ppf "Pcf_val %a\n" fmt_mutable_flag mf;
  613.       line (i+1) ppf "%a\n" fmt_string_loc s;
  614.       class_field_kind (i+1) ppf k
  615.   | Pcf_method (s, pf, k) ->
  616.       line i ppf "Pcf_method %a\n" fmt_private_flag pf;
  617.       line (i+1) ppf "%a\n" fmt_string_loc s;
  618.       class_field_kind (i+1) ppf k
  619.   | Pcf_constraint (ct1, ct2) ->
  620.       line i ppf "Pcf_constraint\n";
  621.       core_type (i+1) ppf ct1;
  622.       core_type (i+1) ppf ct2;
  623.   | Pcf_initializer (e) ->
  624.       line i ppf "Pcf_initializer\n";
  625.       expression (i+1) ppf e;
  626.   | Pcf_attribute a ->
  627.       attribute i ppf "Pcf_attribute" a
  628.   | Pcf_extension (s, arg) ->
  629.       line i ppf "Pcf_extension \"%s\"\n" s.txt;
  630.       payload i ppf arg

  632. and class_field_kind i ppf = function
  633.   | Cfk_concrete (o, e) ->
  634.       line i ppf "Concrete %a\n" fmt_override_flag o;
  635.       expression i ppf e
  636.   | Cfk_virtual t ->
  637.       line i ppf "Virtual\n";
  638.       core_type i ppf t

  640. and class_declaration i ppf x =
  641.   line i ppf "class_declaration %a\n" fmt_location x.pci_loc;
  642.   attributes i ppf x.pci_attributes;
  643.   let i = i+1 in
  644.   line i ppf "pci_virt = %a\n" fmt_virtual_flag x.pci_virt;
  645.   line i ppf "pci_params =\n";
  646.   list (i+1) type_parameter ppf x.pci_params;
  647.   line i ppf "pci_name = %a\n" fmt_string_loc x.pci_name;
  648.   line i ppf "pci_expr =\n";
  649.   class_expr (i+1) ppf x.pci_expr;

  651. and module_type i ppf x =
  652.   line i ppf "module_type %a\n" fmt_location x.pmty_loc;
  653.   attributes i ppf x.pmty_attributes;
  654.   let i = i+1 in
  655.   match x.pmty_desc with
  656.   | Pmty_ident li -> line i ppf "Pmty_ident %a\n" fmt_longident_loc li;
  657.   | Pmty_alias li -> line i ppf "Pmty_alias %a\n" fmt_longident_loc li;
  658.   | Pmty_signature (s) ->
  659.       line i ppf "Pmty_signature\n";
  660.       signature i ppf s;
  661.   | Pmty_functor (Unit, mt2) ->
  662.       line i ppf "Pmty_functor ()\n";
  663.       module_type i ppf mt2;
  664.   | Pmty_functor (Named (s, mt1), mt2) ->
  665.       line i ppf "Pmty_functor %a\n" fmt_str_opt_loc s;
  666.       module_type i ppf mt1;
  667.       module_type i ppf mt2;
  668.   | Pmty_with (mt, l) ->
  669.       line i ppf "Pmty_with\n";
  670.       module_type i ppf mt;
  671.       list i with_constraint ppf l;
  672.   | Pmty_typeof m ->
  673.       line i ppf "Pmty_typeof\n";
  674.       module_expr i ppf m;
  675.   | Pmty_extension (s, arg) ->
  676.       line i ppf "Pmod_extension \"%s\"\n" s.txt;
  677.       payload i ppf arg

  679. and signature i ppf x = list i signature_item ppf x

  681. and signature_item i ppf x =
  682.   line i ppf "signature_item %a\n" fmt_location x.psig_loc;
  683.   let i = i+1 in
  684.   match x.psig_desc with
  685.   | Psig_value vd ->
  686.       line i ppf "Psig_value\n";
  687.       value_description i ppf vd;
  688.   | Psig_type (rf, l) ->
  689.       line i ppf "Psig_type %a\n" fmt_rec_flag rf;
  690.       list i type_declaration ppf l;
  691.   | Psig_typesubst l ->
  692.       line i ppf "Psig_typesubst\n";
  693.       list i type_declaration ppf l;
  694.   | Psig_typext te ->
  695.       line i ppf "Psig_typext\n";
  696.       type_extension i ppf te
  697.   | Psig_exception te ->
  698.       line i ppf "Psig_exception\n";
  699.       type_exception i ppf te
  700.   | Psig_module pmd ->
  701.       line i ppf "Psig_module %a\n" fmt_str_opt_loc pmd.pmd_name;
  702.       attributes i ppf pmd.pmd_attributes;
  703.       module_type i ppf pmd.pmd_type
  704.   | Psig_modsubst pms ->
  705.       line i ppf "Psig_modsubst %a = %a\n"
  706.         fmt_string_loc pms.pms_name
  707.         fmt_longident_loc pms.pms_manifest;
  708.       attributes i ppf pms.pms_attributes;
  709.   | Psig_recmodule decls ->
  710.       line i ppf "Psig_recmodule\n";
  711.       list i module_declaration ppf decls;
  712.   | Psig_modtype x ->
  713.       line i ppf "Psig_modtype %a\n" fmt_string_loc x.pmtd_name;
  714.       attributes i ppf x.pmtd_attributes;
  715.       modtype_declaration i ppf x.pmtd_type
  716.   | Psig_modtypesubst x ->
  717.       line i ppf "Psig_modtypesubst %a\n" fmt_string_loc x.pmtd_name;
  718.       attributes i ppf x.pmtd_attributes;
  719.       modtype_declaration i ppf x.pmtd_type
  720.   | Psig_open od ->
  721.       line i ppf "Psig_open %a %a\n" fmt_override_flag od.popen_override
  722.         fmt_longident_loc od.popen_expr;
  723.       attributes i ppf od.popen_attributes
  724.   | Psig_include incl ->
  725.       line i ppf "Psig_include\n";
  726.       module_type i ppf incl.pincl_mod;
  727.       attributes i ppf incl.pincl_attributes
  728.   | Psig_class (l) ->
  729.       line i ppf "Psig_class\n";
  730.       list i class_description ppf l;
  731.   | Psig_class_type (l) ->
  732.       line i ppf "Psig_class_type\n";
  733.       list i class_type_declaration ppf l;
  734.   | Psig_extension ((s, arg), attrs) ->
  735.       line i ppf "Psig_extension \"%s\"\n" s.txt;
  736.       attributes i ppf attrs;
  737.       payload i ppf arg
  738.   | Psig_attribute a ->
  739.       attribute i ppf "Psig_attribute" a

  741. and modtype_declaration i ppf = function
  742.   | None -> line i ppf "#abstract"
  743.   | Some mt -> module_type (i+1) ppf mt

  745. and with_constraint i ppf x =
  746.   match x with
  747.   | Pwith_type (lid, td) ->
  748.       line i ppf "Pwith_type %a\n" fmt_longident_loc lid;
  749.       type_declaration (i+1) ppf td;
  750.   | Pwith_typesubst (lid, td) ->
  751.       line i ppf "Pwith_typesubst %a\n" fmt_longident_loc lid;
  752.       type_declaration (i+1) ppf td;
  753.   | Pwith_module (lid1, lid2) ->
  754.       line i ppf "Pwith_module %a = %a\n"
  755.         fmt_longident_loc lid1
  756.         fmt_longident_loc lid2;
  757.   | Pwith_modsubst (lid1, lid2) ->
  758.       line i ppf "Pwith_modsubst %a = %a\n"
  759.         fmt_longident_loc lid1
  760.         fmt_longident_loc lid2;
  761.   | Pwith_modtype (lid1, mty) ->
  762.       line i ppf "Pwith_modtype %a\n"
  763.         fmt_longident_loc lid1;
  764.       module_type (i+1) ppf mty
  765.   | Pwith_modtypesubst (lid1, mty) ->
  766.      line i ppf "Pwith_modtypesubst %a\n"
  767.         fmt_longident_loc lid1;
  768.       module_type (i+1) ppf mty

  770. and module_expr i ppf x =
  771.   line i ppf "module_expr %a\n" fmt_location x.pmod_loc;
  772.   attributes i ppf x.pmod_attributes;
  773.   let i = i+1 in
  774.   match x.pmod_desc with
  775.   | Pmod_ident (li) -> line i ppf "Pmod_ident %a\n" fmt_longident_loc li;
  776.   | Pmod_structure (s) ->
  777.       line i ppf "Pmod_structure\n";
  778.       structure i ppf s;
  779.   | Pmod_functor (Unit, me) ->
  780.       line i ppf "Pmod_functor ()\n";
  781.       module_expr i ppf me;
  782.   | Pmod_functor (Named (s, mt), me) ->
  783.       line i ppf "Pmod_functor %a\n" fmt_str_opt_loc s;
  784.       module_type i ppf mt;
  785.       module_expr i ppf me;
  786.   | Pmod_apply (me1, me2) ->
  787.       line i ppf "Pmod_apply\n";
  788.       module_expr i ppf me1;
  789.       module_expr i ppf me2;
  790.   | Pmod_apply_unit me1 ->
  791.       line i ppf "Pmod_apply_unit\n";
  792.       module_expr i ppf me1
  793.   | Pmod_constraint (me, mt) ->
  794.       line i ppf "Pmod_constraint\n";
  795.       module_expr i ppf me;
  796.       module_type i ppf mt;
  797.   | Pmod_unpack (e) ->
  798.       line i ppf "Pmod_unpack\n";
  799.       expression i ppf e;
  800.   | Pmod_extension (s, arg) ->
  801.       line i ppf "Pmod_extension \"%s\"\n" s.txt;
  802.       payload i ppf arg

  804. and structure i ppf x = list i structure_item ppf x

  806. and structure_item i ppf x =
  807.   line i ppf "structure_item %a\n" fmt_location x.pstr_loc;
  808.   let i = i+1 in
  809.   match x.pstr_desc with
  810.   | Pstr_eval (e, attrs) ->
  811.       line i ppf "Pstr_eval\n";
  812.       attributes i ppf attrs;
  813.       expression i ppf e;
  814.   | Pstr_value (rf, l) ->
  815.       line i ppf "Pstr_value %a\n" fmt_rec_flag rf;
  816.       list i value_binding ppf l;
  817.   | Pstr_primitive vd ->
  818.       line i ppf "Pstr_primitive\n";
  819.       value_description i ppf vd;
  820.   | Pstr_type (rf, l) ->
  821.       line i ppf "Pstr_type %a\n" fmt_rec_flag rf;
  822.       list i type_declaration ppf l;
  823.   | Pstr_typext te ->
  824.       line i ppf "Pstr_typext\n";
  825.       type_extension i ppf te
  826.   | Pstr_exception te ->
  827.       line i ppf "Pstr_exception\n";
  828.       type_exception i ppf te
  829.   | Pstr_module x ->
  830.       line i ppf "Pstr_module\n";
  831.       module_binding i ppf x
  832.   | Pstr_recmodule bindings ->
  833.       line i ppf "Pstr_recmodule\n";
  834.       list i module_binding ppf bindings;
  835.   | Pstr_modtype x ->
  836.       line i ppf "Pstr_modtype %a\n" fmt_string_loc x.pmtd_name;
  837.       attributes i ppf x.pmtd_attributes;
  838.       modtype_declaration i ppf x.pmtd_type
  839.   | Pstr_open od ->
  840.       line i ppf "Pstr_open %a\n" fmt_override_flag od.popen_override;
  841.       module_expr i ppf od.popen_expr;
  842.       attributes i ppf od.popen_attributes
  843.   | Pstr_class (l) ->
  844.       line i ppf "Pstr_class\n";
  845.       list i class_declaration ppf l;
  846.   | Pstr_class_type (l) ->
  847.       line i ppf "Pstr_class_type\n";
  848.       list i class_type_declaration ppf l;
  849.   | Pstr_include incl ->
  850.       line i ppf "Pstr_include";
  851.       attributes i ppf incl.pincl_attributes;
  852.       module_expr i ppf incl.pincl_mod
  853.   | Pstr_extension ((s, arg), attrs) ->
  854.       line i ppf "Pstr_extension \"%s\"\n" s.txt;
  855.       attributes i ppf attrs;
  856.       payload i ppf arg
  857.   | Pstr_attribute a ->
  858.       attribute i ppf "Pstr_attribute" a

  860. and module_declaration i ppf pmd =
  861.   str_opt_loc i ppf pmd.pmd_name;
  862.   attributes i ppf pmd.pmd_attributes;
  863.   module_type (i+1) ppf pmd.pmd_type;

  865. and module_binding i ppf x =
  866.   str_opt_loc i ppf x.pmb_name;
  867.   attributes i ppf x.pmb_attributes;
  868.   module_expr (i+1) ppf x.pmb_expr

  870. and core_type_x_core_type_x_location i ppf (ct1, ct2, l) =
  871.   line i ppf "<constraint> %a\n" fmt_location l;
  872.   core_type (i+1) ppf ct1;
  873.   core_type (i+1) ppf ct2;

  875. and constructor_decl i ppf
  876.      {pcd_name; pcd_vars; pcd_args; pcd_res; pcd_loc; pcd_attributes} =
